wsdl:operation.name: GetAvailableRoutes
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to give the list of routes going from the specified source city to the destination city and seats available on the specified date.

wsdl:operation.name: GetSeatLayout
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to give the seat layout for the specified route

wsdl:operation.name: GetNewSeatLayout
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to give the new seat layout for the specified route

wsdl:operation.name: GetBoardingPoints
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to give the list of boarding points , times,lcation,address,contactnumber and location for the specified route

wsdl:operation.name: DoTentativeBooking
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to book a ticket tentatively.This ticket may be confirmed after the payment is made. Here the seats are blocked only for a specified time after which then cannot be confirmed.

wsdl:operation.name: DoTentativeBookingV2
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to book a ticket tentatively.This ticket may be confirmed after the payment is made. Here the seats are blocked only for a specified time after which then cannot be confirmed.

wsdl:operation.name: CancelTentativeBooking
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to cancel the given tentative booking reference number.

wsdl:operation.name: ConfirmTicket
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to give confirm the tentatively booked ticket

wsdl:operation.name: TicketRequest
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to take ticket request for the specified route and DateofJourney

wsdl:operation.name: GetDroppingPoints
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to give the list of dropping points , times,lcation,address,contactnumber and location for the specified route

wsdl:operation.name: GetRouteDetails
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: API to give the route details for the specified route
